Starts or restarts the game server. Optional with restart message for restart.log.  Request:  POST /services/ id /gameservers/restart?access_token= access_token   POST Parameters:  message=This is a restart command (optional)  Response:  {
   status :  success ,
   message :  Server will be restarted now 
}

Stopps the game server. Optional with stop message for restart.log  Request:  POST /services/ id /gameservers/stop?access_token= access_token   POST Parameters:  message=This is a stop command (optional)  Response:  {
   status :  success ,
   message :  Server will be stopped now 
}

Changes the ftp password from the gameserver.  Request:  POST /services/ id /gameservers/ftp/password?access_token= access_token   POST Parameters:  password=ChestersMill  Response:  {
   status :  success ,
   message :  The ftp password has been changed 
}

Changes the MySQL password from the gameservers database.  Request:  POST /services/ id /gameservers/mysql/password?access_token= access_token   POST Parameters:  password=ChestersMill  Response:  {
   status :  success ,
   message :  The MySQL database password has been changed 
}

Truncates the MySQL database of the gameserver. Optionally you can set a new password.  Request:  POST /services/ id /gameservers/mysql/reset?access_token= access_token   POST Parameters:  password=ChestersMill (optional)  Response:  {
   status :  success ,
   message :  The MySQL database has been reset 
}

Updates a value of a specific setting.  Request:  POST /services/ id /gameservers/settings?access_token= access_token   POST Parameter:  category=config
key=mysetting
value=true  Response:  {
    status : success ,
    data :{
       settings :{
          config :{
             mysetting : true 
         }
      }
   }
}

