Creates a new config set with the current settings.  Request:  POST /services/ id /gameservers/settings/sets?access_token= access_token   POST Parameter:  name=My new config set (optional)  Response:  {
    status : success ,
    message : Set has been created 
}

Deletes a specific config set.  Request:  DELETE /services/ id /gameservers/settings/sets/ id ?access_token= access_token   Response:  {
    status : success ,
    message : Set has been deleted 
}

Restores a specific config set.  Request:  POST /services/ id /gameservers/settings/sets/ id /restore?access_token= access_token   Response:  {
    status : success ,
    message : Set has been restored 
}

