}

Updates a existing scheduled task for the service.  Request:  POST /services/ id /gameservers/tasks/ id ?access_token= access_token   POST Parameter:  action_method=stop  Response:  {
    status : success ,
    message : Task has been updated 
}

Deletes the specific scheduled task for the service.  Request:  DELETE /services/ id /gameservers/tasks/ id ?access_token= access_token   Response:  {
    status : success ,
    message : The task has been deleted 
}

